\s4 Northern kingdom
\p
\v 30 ThenВҰ177135 YehuВҰ177136 cameВҰ177135 to Yizre'el and \add Queen\add* Izevel \add (Jezebel)\add* heardВҰ177139 \add about it\add*. She \add вүҲpaintedВҰ177141 her eyelids\add* and \add вүҲdid her hair nicely\add*, thenВҰ177135 she lookedВҰ177147 \add down\add* throughВҰ177148 the windowВҰ177149,
\v 31 andВҰ177154 \add when\add* Yehu cameВҰ177152 inВҰ177153 the gateВҰ177153, she saidВҰ177154, вҖңGreetings, ZimriВҰ177156 \add the second\add*,\x + \xo 9:31: \xt 1Ki 16:10.\x* murdererВҰ177157 of his masterВҰ177158.вҖқ
\v 32 \add @Yehu\add* \add вүҲlooked up at\add* the windowВҰ177164 and \add вүҲcalled out\add*, вҖңWho is with me? Who?вҖқ And two or threeВҰ177172 servants \add poked their heads out windows and\add* looked down to him.
\v 33 вҖң\add Okay,\add*вҖқ he \add вүҲcalled up\add*, вҖң\add вүҲtoss her out\add*!вҖқ
\p \add вүҲSoВҰ177175\add* they tossed her \add out the window\add*, and some of her bloodВҰ177180 splashed onto the wall and onto the horsesВҰ177186 \add вүҲas she was trampledВҰ177187 by them\add*.
\v 34 ThenВҰ177189 \add @Yehu\add* \add and his men\add* wentВҰ177189 in and ateВҰ177190 and drankВҰ177191, and thenВҰ177189 he saidВҰ177192, вҖң\add вүҲNowВҰ177196,\add* you all better attendВҰ177193 to that \add вүҲevil\add* woman and buryВҰ177200 her, because she's a king's daughterВҰ177202.вҖқ
\v 35 \add вүҲButВҰ177207 when\add* they wentВҰ177207 to buryВҰ177208 her, they \add вүҲcould only find\add* her skullВҰ177216 and her handsВҰ177219 and feetВҰ177217.
\v 36 They \add вүҲcame back inside\add* andВҰ177221 told him, вҖңIt's just like what YahwehВҰ177227 said via his servantВҰ177233 the TishbiteВҰ177235 EliyahВҰ177234, when he said thatВҰ177229 the dogs would eat Izevel's fleshВҰ177243 \add вүҲjust outside\add* Yizre'el,
\v 37 and thenВҰ177246 \add *her\add* body would become like dung onВҰ177255 the \add вүҲground and no one would be able to recognise her specific bones\add*.вҖқ
\c 10
\s1 Ahab's descendants are eliminated
\rem /s1 The Descendants of Ahab Are Killed; Massacre of Ahab's Descendants; Ahab's Family Killed; Jehu Kills Ahab's Family
\s4 Northern kingdom
\p
\v 1 \add King\add* Ahab had seventyВҰ177266 sonsВҰ177267 who lived inВҰ177268 Shomron \add (SamariaВҰ177268)\add*, \add вүҲso\add* YehuВҰ177270 sentВҰ177272 lettersВҰ177271 to the leaders and eldersВҰ177278 of Yizre'el, and to the guardiansВҰ177281 of Ahab'sВҰ177265 children, saying,
\v 2 вҖңWhenВҰ177285 you all \add вүҲreceive\add* this letterВҰ177287, \add вүҲyou'll have\add* the sonsВҰ177291 of your mastersВҰ177292 \add вүҲwith you, as well as\add* chariotsВҰ177294 and horsesВҰ177295, and weaponsВҰ177298 \add within your\add* fortifiedВҰ177297 cityВҰ177296.
\v 3 \add вүҲSoВҰ177300 selectВҰ177300\add* the best and the most honest one out of your masters' sonsВҰ177303 \add or nephews\add*, and \add вүҲestablish\add* him on his father'sВҰ177309 throneВҰ177308, and thenВҰ177300 \add вүҲbe prepared to defend your masters' family\add*.вҖқ
\v 4 \add вүҲButВҰ177316\add* they were extremely frightened andВҰ177316 saidВҰ177319, вҖңListenвҖ”those twoВҰ177321 kingsВҰ177322 couldn't standВҰ177327 \add вүҲagainst Yehu, so how could\add* we?вҖқ
\v 5 ThenВҰ177330 the man who was \add now\add* inВҰ177360 charge of the household and leading the cityВҰ177339 eldersВҰ177340 sentВҰ177330 \add a message\add* to YehuВҰ177344, вҖңWe are yourВҰ177360 servantsВҰ177347 and we'll do whatever you tell us to. We don'tВҰ177355 \add вүҲplan to select a\add* kingВҰ177357. Do \add вүҲwhatever you think best\add*.вҖқ
\p
\v 6 \add вүҲSoВҰ177363\add* \add @Yehu\add* \add вүҲsent\add* a secondВҰ177367 letterВҰ177365 saying, вҖңIf you're all \add вүҲon myВҰ177373 side and ready to follow\add* me, come and meet me at Yizre'el tomorrowВҰ177388 with the headsВҰ177380 of your masters' sons.вҖқ
\p \add вүҲThe late KingВҰ177391 Ahab had\add* seventyВҰ177392 sons \add вүҲwho were being brought up by the cityВҰ177397 leaders\add*,
\v 7 and when that letterВҰ177403 \add вүҲarrived\add*, theyВҰ177405 killed and beheaded all of them, put the headsВҰ177416 inВҰ177417 basketsВҰ177417, and sentВҰ177418 them to him atВҰ177417 Yizre'elВҰ177420.
\p
\v 8 AВҰ177435 messengerВҰ177423 wentВҰ177422 and informed \add @Yehu\add* that the headsВҰ177429 had been broughtВҰ177428, and he instructed them to pile them up in twoВҰ177436 piles at the \add city\add* gateВҰ177439 untilВҰ177440 the next morningВҰ177442.
\v 9 In the morningВҰ177445 he wentВҰ177446 out and stoodВҰ177447 there, and he told all the peopleВҰ177453, вҖңYou are innocent. ListenвҖ”it was me myself who conspiredВҰ177458 against my masterВҰ177461 and killed him. ButВҰ177444 who killed all theseВҰ177469?
\v 10 \add You all should\add* know that \add вүҲwhen YahwehВҰ177477 says something will happen, then it will happen\add*. \add *He\add* \add вүҲsaid via his servantВҰ177493 EliyahВҰ177494 that this is what would happen to Ahab'sВҰ177486 family, and so it has\add*.вҖқ
\v 11 ThenВҰ177496 YehuВҰ177497 \add вүҲkilledВҰ177496 all Ahab'sВҰ177504 remainingВҰ177501 family members\add* inВҰ177505 Yizre'elВҰ177505, and all \add вүҲhis chosen leaders, and his associates\add* and priestsВҰ177510, leaving no survivorsВҰ177517.
\s1 The relatives of Ahazyah are killed
