\s4 Northern kingdom
\p
\v 12 ThenВҰ177519 \add @Yehu\add* left \add Yizre'el\add* andВҰ177519 headed towards ShomronВҰ177522 \add (Samaria)\add*. \add вүҲWhenВҰ177519 heВҰ177523 reached\add* the shepherds' shearing houseВҰ177524,
\v 13 \add *he\add* \add вүҲmet\add* the \add late\add* King Ahazyah'sВҰ177535 brothers \add there\add*, and he \add вүҲasked\add* \add >them\add*, вҖңWho are you?вҖқ
\p вҖңWe're \add King\add* Ahazyah's brothers,вҖқ they said, вҖңand we're coming \add вүҲto look after\add* the sons of the king and of the queenВҰ177552 motherВҰ177552.вҖқ
\p
\v 14 вҖң\add вүҲArrest\add* them,вҖқ he \add вүҲordered\add*, so they \add вүҲgrabbed\add* and slaughteredВҰ177559 them near the pit at the shearing houseВҰ177563. There were forty-two men and \add вүҲnone were sparedВҰ177571\add*.
\s1 All Ahab's other relatives are killed
\rem /s1 All Remaining Relatives of Ahab Are Killed
\s4 Northern kingdom
\p
\v 15 Then \add вүҲcontinuing on\add* from there, \add @Yehu\add* found Rekav's son Yonadav \add coming\add* to meet him. \add Yehu\add* \add вүҲgreetedВҰ177586 him and asked\add*, вҖң\add вүҲAre you wanting to do what is rightВҰ177593 just like I am\add*?вҖқ IS THAT WHAT HE WAS REALLY ASKING???
\p вҖң\add Yes,\add* \add вүҲI am\add*.вҖқ Yonadav \add вүҲreplied\add*.
\p вҖң\add вүҲGreat\add*,вҖқ \add @Yehu\add* said. вҖңGive me yourВҰ177598 hand,вҖқ and he gave him his hand, and \add @Yehu\add* \add вүҲpulled him up to join him\add* in the chariotВҰ177613,
\v 16 telling \add >him\add*, вҖңComeВҰ177622 withВҰ177619 me andВҰ177615 seeВҰ177618 my zeal for YahwehВҰ177620.вҖқ \add вүҲSoВҰ177615 they rode together inВҰ177619 the\add* chariotВҰ177623.
\v 17 \add вүҲWhenВҰ177625 they got\add* to Shomron, \add @Yehu\add* \add вүҲkilledВҰ177627 the remainderВҰ177632 of Ahab'sВҰ177633 family who were there\add*, untilВҰ177635 \add вүҲthey were finally\add* exterminated, \add вүҲjust as YahwehВҰ177639 had said via\add* EliyahВҰ177644.
\p
\rem /s1 The Worshippers of Baal Are Killed; Slaughter of Worshippers of Baal; Jehu Kills the Priests of Baal; Ministers of Baal Killed
\v 18 Then Yehu assembledВҰ177647 all the peopleВҰ177653 and told them, вҖңAhabВҰ177656 servedВҰ177657 BaalВҰ177660 a littleВҰ177661, \add butВҰ177647\add* Yehu will serveВҰ177663 himВҰ177663 \add вүҲa lot\add*.
\v 19 \add вүҲSoВҰ177666\add* now, call all the prophetsВҰ177669 of Baal to come hereвҖ”all his servants andВҰ177666 all his priestsВҰ177676. Don't let \add вүҲanyoneВҰ177679 stay away because I'm going to make\add* a large sacrificeВҰ177684 to Baal. \add вүҲAnyone who's absent will be executed\add*.вҖқ \add вүҲHowever\add* YehuВҰ177694 \add вүҲwas being\add* cunningВҰ177696 inВҰ177696 order to destroyВҰ177698 Baal'sВҰ177670 \add вүҲfollowers\add*.
\v 20 YehuВҰ177705 \add вүҲordered\add*, вҖң\add вүҲAnnounce a special holiday to assembleВҰ177707\add* \add and worship\add* BaalВҰ177708,вҖқ and \add вүҲso they did\add*.
\v 21 \add On that day,\add* YehuВҰ177712 brought in all \add вүҲthe people\add*, and all the servants of the Baal came, \add вүҲleaving no one out\add*. They entered the \add вүҲtemple\add* of the Baal and \add *it\add* was \add вүҲpacked full\add*.
\v 22 He \add вүҲtold the wardrobeВҰ177743 supervisor\add*, вҖңBring out \add вүҲuniforms\add* for all the servants of the BaalВҰ177748,вҖқ so he broughtВҰ177749 robes out for them.
\v 23 ThenВҰ177753 YehuВҰ177754 and Rekav's son Yonadab entered the \add вүҲtemple\add* of the Baal and \add вүҲinstructed\add* the servants of the Baal, вҖң\add вүҲMake sure that it's only the servants of Baal in hereвҖ”we don't want any\add* servants of YahwehВҰ177773.вҖқ
\v 24 \add вүҲSoВҰ177781\add* they entered to make sacrificesВҰ177783 and burntВҰ177784 offeringsВҰ177784.
\p \add вүҲMeanwhile,\add* YehuВҰ177785 \add вүҲhad stationedВҰ177786\add* eightyВҰ177790 men outsideВҰ177789, and had told \add >them\add*, вҖң\add вүҲDon't let any of the ones I send you escapeВҰ177796, or it will be \em your\em* life inВҰ177789 placeВҰ177807 of theirs\add*.вҖқ
\p
\v 25 Then when he finishedВҰ177811 making the burntВҰ177814 offeringВҰ177814 \add in the outer area\add*, YehuВҰ177816 told the \add вүҲguards\add* and officers, вҖң\add Come in now and\add* strike them \add down\add*. Don't let \add вүҲany of them get\add* out.вҖқ \add вүҲSoВҰ177810\add* they \add вүҲattacked them with swordsВҰ177828\add*, and the \add вүҲguards\add* and officers threwВҰ177829 \add вүҲthe bodies over the fence\add*. Then they went \add вүҲinside the temple\add*,
\v 26 and pulled the \add вүҲsacredВҰ177843 posts\add* outside and burnt \add #them\add*.
\v 27 They broke down the pillarВҰ177851 of the BaalВҰ177852, andВҰ177849 they broke down the \add вүҲtemple\add*. \add вүҲSince thenВҰ177849 it's been used as an out-house\add*.
\p
\v 28 \add That's how\add* YehuВҰ177866 \add вүҲput an end to BaalВҰ177869 worship in\add* YisraelВҰ177870.
\v 29 \add вүҲThere was only one of the things withВҰ177895 which Nebat'sВҰ177877 son Yarave'amВҰ177874 had causedВҰ177879 YisraelВҰ177882 to sinВҰ177879 thatВҰ177878 YehuВҰ177886 didn'tВҰ177883 destroy\add*: the golden calvesВҰ177888 atВҰ177895 Beyt-El andВҰ177894 DanВҰ177895.
\v 30 Then YahwehВҰ177899 told YehuВҰ177902, вҖңBecause you did good by \add вүҲfollowing my principles and doingВҰ177907 what I've saidВҰ177898 is rightВҰ177908, including what you did to Ahab'sВҰ177915 family, you'll have four generationsВҰ177917 sitting onВҰ177909 Yisrael'sВҰ177923 throneВҰ177922\add*.вҖқ
\v 31 \add вүҲButВҰ177925\add* Yehu didn't take care \add вүҲto follow the instructions of Yisrael'sВҰ177934 godВҰ177932 YahwehВҰ177931 whole-heartedly\add*вҖ”he didn't \add вүҲreject all of Yarave'am's evil customs\add* whichВҰ177943 had causedВҰ177944 Yisrael to sinВҰ177944.
\s1 Yehu's death
