\v 1 \add вүҲBy that time,\add* \add King\add* Hizkiyah was \add вүҲterminally ill\add* and Amots's son the prophetВҰ183657 Yeshayah \add (IsaiahВҰ183653)\add* came to him and told him, вҖңYahwehВҰ183663 says to \add вүҲget your affairs in order\add* because you're dying and \add вүҲwon'tВҰ183669 recover\add*.вҖқ
