\v 6 He's added fifteen years to your life, plus he'll rescue you and this city from the Assyrian king. \add @Yahweh\add* will defendВҰ183767 \add @Yerushalem\add* for his own sake and for the sake of his servantВҰ183775 DavidВҰ183774.вҖқ
\p
